- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with video analysis and action recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an online optimization algorithm for weakly supervised learning. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is another possible category as the paper involves text-to-video alignment. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with clustering in videos and images. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also possible as the paper involves searching for relevant information in movie scripts.
